_sText: Godzillawars Source Alpha 1 Pseudo Story: Evil Terrorists foundet their Evil Terrorist Camp on a little Island. But then the American Government tested Nuclear Weapons on the Island. Some of the Terrorists not died in these Tests, and now theyre Mutated into Giant Terrorists and want to rule the World. The Only Chance for the Government is to make a force of Nuclear Counter-Terrorists to beat them. Now the Terrorists are on their way to a city, but this time they get unexpected Guests. Map by: Gandorques Hikla Clan: Professionals E-Mail: OverlordXL@lycos.de Clanpage: http://www.rm2k-tv.de/vwar Clan Forum: http://www.rm2k-tv.de/professionals/index.php Check out for more of my Maps: www.hl2files.com Clanserver: 84.16.230.126:28100 Special thanks to AriesT, Big J, Xelrath, Stick33r, Lupus, Sparkfist, Snoopy, Jake, Snake, Cyb3r, KHUISDE, Bojangles, Tim, Heff, my Brothers, HL2files.com and everyone else who give me Mapping Inspiration. Other info Godzillawars Source Map Title: godzillawars_source_a1 (Godzillawars Source Alpha 1) Type: Funmap Author: Gandorques Hikla from the Professionals Clan E-Mail: OverlordXL@lycos.de Clanpage: http://www.rm2k-tv.de/vwar/ Install Instructions: Extract to "Steam\SteamApps\username\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps" Description: A city, the Terrorists spawn is on the coast, the Counter-Terrorists Spawn is in the City. All Buildings are destroyable and can fall apart (and also can slam players). Good jumpers can also get on higher Buildings. The only objective is to kill the other Team.
